  <p class="post-author">        <a href="/authors/abby-rapoport">Abby Rapoport</a>  </p>  
          <p class="post-date">October 15, 2012</p>    
          <div class="post-teaser"> <p>The organization obsessed with voter fraud may sell itself as nonpartisan, but its Republican leanings are easy to spot.</p>
 </div>    
